(189, 632, 1, NULL, 'BEEF CUTTING PROJECT', NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bachok is one of the district from Kelantan that have beautiful nature.\r\nThe beaches and beautiful scenery are common if you come to Bachok.\r\nThe main source of economic are agriculture. Besides farming, the locals are actively breeding the livestock. The different types of cows and goats are part of the daily life here in Bachok.\r\nThe locals are selling the fresh beef by the roadside. However, none of them sell the beef that have different cut for steak, barbeque, steamboat from a different cut.\r\nThe main objective for this project is to empower the local people in beef supply with different cut for different purpose', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1717831770, 1717831770, '2024-06-08 15:29:31'),
