(200, 640, 1, NULL, 'Unreel Pangkor', NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Unreel Pangkor, an initiative dedicated to promote the cultural conservation and living heritage of local trades on the Island. Since July 2023, our team has organized a series of programs including creative archival, outreach programs, and homecoming exhibitions, transforming an active anchovy fishery and boat factory into living museums. Our participatory live-building project is to integrated permanent archival displays, making heritage preservation an immersive experience. Preserving Pangkor\'s living heritage should be while it’s still thriving to ensure that future generations, the public, and the local community can continue to access and appreciate the industrial heritage in its authenticity.', 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1717833872, 1718077975, '2024-06-11 11:52:55'),
