(268, 646, 1, NULL, 'ReCycle, ReUse, ReRide : Pedal Into a Greener Future', NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This CSR Program established a Used Bikes Recycling Program aimed at providing\r\nused bicycles to underprivileged rural communities such as at machang, kelantan\r\nwhile at the same time promoting environmental sustainability.\r\nthe program collects, refurbishes, and distributes used bicycles, thus reducing\r\nwaste and offering a cost-effective, eco-friendly transportation solution. this\r\nprogram will also offer maintenance services for the underprivileged who\r\ncannot afford to repair their bicycles.\r\nOBJECTIVES:\r\nProvide Affordable Transportation & Healthier Lifestyle: Offer bicycles to\r\nunderprivileged individuals, enhancing their mobility &access to essential\r\nservices and encouraging to have more outdoor activity.\r\nEnvironmental Conservation: Reduce the number of bicycles ending up in\r\nlandfills by refurbishing and reusing them.\r\nCommunity Engagement: Involve local communities in recycling efforts,\r\nfostering a sense of community and shared responsibility for the\r\nenvironment.', 1, NULL, NULL, 88.33, 80, 0, 1717846294, 1717846294, '2024-06-08 19:31:34'),
