(278, 703, 1, NULL, 'Lowering Plastic Impact on the Environment via 5R Module (Refuse, Reduce, Reuse, Recycle, and Recover (LPIE5R)', NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The LPIE5R program aims to raise awareness and educate about environmental sustainability and solid waste management, particularly plastic waste. Exposure and early education to school students regarding the 5R practice is an initiative that can solve the problem of piles of discarded goods around the school or in the area where they live. This project directly encourages students as well as the local community to recycle used waste.', 2, NULL, NULL, 0.00, 0, 0, 1717849669, 1717849669, '2024-06-08 20:27:49'),
