(474, 692, 1, NULL, 'EMPOWERING MOTHERS THROUGH ARTISAN KNOWLEDGE (EMAK)', NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'In many villages surrounding our strategic partner factory (By Che Fiza Sdn. Bhd), mothers and housewives often face limited employment opportunities that fit within their schedules and responsibilities. This project aims to provide these women with a sustainable source of income by utilizing leftover fabric and cloth patchwork from By Che Fiza\'s apparel production. By transforming these materials into marketable products, we seek to empower these women economically while promoting sustainable practices in the fashion industry', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1717867032, 1717867032, '2024-06-09 01:17:12'),
