(555, 955, 1, NULL, 'Agropreneurs in Grey Oyster Mushrooms cultivation a powerful tool for empowering indigenous communities in Sg. Rual, Jeli, Kelantan', NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The Orang Asli community in Sg. Rual faces significant poverty due to limited access to economic opportunities. The Coolat D\'Jeli project was established in 2020 to address this challenge by providing the community with sustainable income through agropreneurship in grey oyster mushroom cultivation.\r\n', 2, NULL, NULL, 92.15, 80, 0, 1717986847, 1717986847, '2024-06-10 10:34:07'),
