(570, 1418, 1, NULL, 'Mango Siasi', NULL, 10, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mango Siasi is a Bumiputra owned agricultural company established in 2013, operating in Kampung Bakung-Bakung, Pulau Lihak-Lihak Semporna, Sabah. The company is registered under the SSM CA0366701-A and specialize in distributing agricultural products, specifially honey mangoes. Mango Siasi\'s primary commercial activities involved selling farm produce from its honey mango plant\r\nprojects in the domestic market. The projects encompasses 40 acres of land with approximately 3000 Mango trees planted since 2013. These trees yield honey mangoes for times a year, contributing to the company production and distribution\r\neffort. Mango Siasi reaching sales of 100 thousand a year.', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1718003999, 1718003999, '2024-06-10 15:19:59'),
